'''清潔能源計劃'''（Clean Power Plan）是美國[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]政府旨在应对气候变化（[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]）而推出的政策，由[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]于2014年6月首次提出<ref>{{Cite web|title=Clean Power Plan for Existing Power Plants|url=http://www2.epa.gov/cleanpowerplan/clean-power-plan-existing-power-plants|accessdate=August 14, 2018|work=EPA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325042337/https://www.epa.gov/cleanpowerplan/clean-power-plan-existing-power-plants|archivedate=March 25, 2016}}</ref>。2015年8月3日，美國總統奥巴马公布了该计划的最终版本<ref name="bbc">{{Cite web|title=Climate change: Obama unveils Clean Power Plan|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33753067|accessdate=August 3, 2015|date=August 3, 2015|work=BBC News|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831060546/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33753067|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據該計劃，美國每个州都被分配了一个单独的减少碳排放的目标，各州可以根據自己合适的方式来達成目標，但如果该州拒绝提交減排计划，[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]就有可能介入<ref>{{Cite web|title=How Obama's Clean Power Plan actually works — a step-by-step guide|url=https://www.vox.com/2015/8/4/9096903/clean-power-plan-explained|author=Plumer|date=4 August 2015|first=Brad|work=[[Vox_(website)|Vox]]|language=en|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401202204/https://www.vox.com/2015/8/4/9096903/clean-power-plan-explained|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如果每个州都完成了目标，那麼到2030年，相对于2005年的水平，美國发电产生的碳排放将减少32%，同时由于空气污染的减少，还能实现各种健康效益。

2017年，美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]签署行政命令，授权环保局审查该计划<ref>{{Citation|title=Trump Lays Plans to Reverse Obama's Climate Change Legacy|last=Coral Davenport|journal=The New York Times|date=March 21, 2017|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/21/climate/trump-climate-change.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214153217/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/21/climate/trump-climate-change.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HillObama_era">{{Cite news|author=Manchester|first=Julia|title=EPA to propose ending Obama-era Clean Power Plan: report|url=http://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/353797-epa-to-propose-ending-obama-era-clean-power-plan-report|work=The Hill|date=4 October 2017|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118202252/https://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/353797-epa-to-propose-ending-obama-era-clean-power-plan-report|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="washpooct6">{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/energy-environment/wp/2017/10/05/trump-administration-will-propose-repealing-obamas-key-effort-to-combat-climate-change/|title=Trump administration will propose repealing Obama's key effort to combat climate change|work=The Washington Post|author=Dennis, Brady|author2=Eilperin, Juliet|date=6 October 2017|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328231226/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/energy-environment/wp/2017/10/05/trump-administration-will-propose-repealing-obamas-key-effort-to-combat-climate-change/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="oct6">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-10-06/trump-seen-replacing-obama-power-plant-overhaul-with-a-tune-up|author=Dlouhy|first=Jennifer A|title=Trump Is Seen Replacing Obama's Power Plant Overhaul With a Tune-Up|work=Bloomberg|date=October 6, 2017|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2019-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102112355/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-10-06/trump-seen-replacing-obama-power-plant-overhaul-with-a-tune-up|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，并宣佈美国退出《[[巴黎協定|巴黎協定]]》<ref>{{Citation|publisher=White House Office of the Press Secretary|title=Background Briefing on the President's Energy Independence Executive Order|date=March 27, 2017|url=https://trumpwhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/2017/03/27/background-briefing-presidents-energy-independence-executive-order}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Trump Signs Executive Order Unwinding Obama Climate Policies|last=Coral Davenport|date=March 28, 2017|journal=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/28/climate/trump-executive-order-climate-change.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426083756/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/28/climate/trump-executive-order-climate-change.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Court Status Aug 2017">{{Cite web|title=Federal Court Extends Suspension Of Clean Power Plan Case|url=http://solarindustrymag.com/federal-court-extends-suspension-clean-power-plan-case|accessdate=August 11, 2017|date=August 9, 2017|publisher=Solar Industry|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811223927/http://solarindustrymag.com/federal-court-extends-suspension-clean-power-plan-case|archivedate=August 11, 2017}}</ref>。特朗普任命的[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]局長[[史考特·普魯特|史考特·普魯特]]宣布，将于2017年10月10日开始啟動废除清洁能源计划的程序<ref name="NYTRepeal">{{Cite news|author=Friedman|first=Lisa|author2=Plumer|first2=Brad|title=E.P.A. Announces Repeal of Major Obama-Era Carbon Emissions Rule|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/09/climate/clean-power-plan.html|work=The New York Times|date=October 9, 2017|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2019-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910162221/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/09/climate/clean-power-plan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="oct710">{{Cite web|title=U.S. to 'Withdraw' Obama-Era Clean Power Plan Tuesday, EPA Head Says|url=https://weather.com/news/climate/news/epa-head-scott-pruitt-says-trump-administration-will-withdraw-from-obama-clean|date=9 October 2017|work=The Weather Channel|publisher=Associated Press|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012071143/https://weather.com/news/climate/news/epa-head-scott-pruitt-says-trump-administration-will-withdraw-from-obama-clean|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

